 Chioma, the girlfriend of music superstar, Davido, has recovered from coronavirus. She tested negative twice after contracting the virus. Davido made this known via his Twitter handle on Sunday evening. He tweeted: “Glory be to God .. Chioma has now tested negative twice for Covid19 … Thank you all for prayers …. We love you ..” Details shortly…   Glory be to God .. Chioma has now tested negative twice for Covid19 … Thank you all for prayers …. We love you .. — Davido (@davido) April 19, 2020  